{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Also, Auschwitz was a society that had more differences, class differences, probably, than any normal society in-- in the free world or not-so-free world.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "We knew that-- you know, I did not come from a classless society.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "We knew that money mattered and that people belonged to different classes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "But that was nothing to prepare you for Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "Those people who had some kind of power, like your block elder for instance, they stole probably half of your rations, if you got a little wurst or anything that was worthwhile stealing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "And they had some kind of a stove where they cooked meals from stuff that they stole from the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And I remember once our bunk bed was right next to the block elder's room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "She was the only one who had a separate room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And there was a crack on the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "These barracks were wooden barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And we could see, and smell through that crack that-- what they were cooking up from the rations that they basically stole from us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "The difference there between a block elder and the rest of us was greater than between the poorest person and nobility in the world that we knew before.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There were random selections, what-- which meant that they would close all the barracks from the outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "We were all ordered to stay in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "And maybe after a couple of hours we would find out how many hundreds of people they took away for the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "I think it was really just numbers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "They needed people to-- to feed the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "After seven weeks under these circumstances I got very ill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "I had a high fever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "My friends tried to hide me behind somebody during roll calls.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
